{
  "stem": "13469.6",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I gather that generally, everything deteriorated, because there were more and more people coming into the camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was just getting overcrowded.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it tended to spread the illnesses, and the medical facilities just weren't up to it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At that time, we hadn't got to the typhus yet.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the typhus epidemic later on really killed many people in Belsen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And again, I don't think our food rations were any less than we'd been getting before Kramer was there, though I wouldn't think that we actually noticed very much, in terms of Kramer arriving there.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it was the general atmosphere and all these other people who were coming into the camp that made everything just generally worse.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't really know, in a way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was just that people started to [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] shout, and-- and be ill, and eventually die.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not in our camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were never beaten in our camp, [INAUDIBLE] So this is really where we were indeed privileged compared to what we've heard about other camps and maybe even other sections of Belsen.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in our camp, I can't remember anybody being beaten or shot, anything like that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we couldn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were in our star camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We couldn't get out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We never mingled with anybody outside the star camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You will see, if you've seen the Anne Frank reconstruction recently, the latest thing, where somebody talked through the wire-- across the wire.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She said that we couldn't see through the wire, that there was cotton cloth or something like that in the wire, so you couldn't see the other camps.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I can't remember that we couldn't see the other camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we certainly couldn't mix with them.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
